gobblin.data.management.policy

Class SelectBetweenTimeBasedPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.policy.SelectBetweenTimeBasedPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VersionSelectionPolicy<TimestampedDatasetVersion>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SelectAfterTimeBasedPolicy, SelectBeforeTimeBasedPolicy

    @Alias(value="SelectBetweenTimeBasedPolicy")
public class SelectBetweenTimeBasedPolicy
extends Object
implements VersionSelectionPolicy<TimestampedDatasetVersion>
    Policy used to select versions in a time range. It selects TimestampedDatasetVersions that are not older than maxLookBackPeriod and not newer than minLookBackPeriod.
    • If minLookbackTime is absent, the current time is used as min lookback
    • If maxLookbackTime is absent, an infinite time is used for max lookback
